frames.caption: A whimsical scene depicts miniature figures working on a large cake adorned with strawberries. The figures, dressed as workers, are using ladders to reach the top of the cake, adding to the playful and imaginative atmosphere.
frames.description: The image portrays a creative and playful setting where tiny figures are engaged in decorating a large, strawberry-topped cake. The scene is reminiscent of a fantasy world where the figures appear to be constructing or embellishing the dessert.

frames.caption: A whimsical scene depicts miniature construction workers decorating a large cake with strawberries and whipped cream. The workers are positioned around the cake, some carrying buckets of cream, while others are climbing ladders to reach the top. Powdered sugar is being sprinkled over the cake, creating a magical snowfall effect.
